    ‚ćĚ no benefit

    ‚ćĚ Case 1:
    acc‚Üź‚ćļ√ó'^'‚Č†cur

    ‚ćĚ Case 2:
    ‚ćĚ We rotate the incoming accumulator ‚ćļ to line up with the
    ‚ćĚ places where we detect the left fork. We can get away
    ‚ćĚ with it since we know the input will always result in
    ‚ćĚ an accumulator with 0's at the edges.
    acc+‚Üź(1‚äĖ‚ćļ)√ó'|^'‚ć∑cur

    ‚ćĚ Case 3:
    ‚ćĚ Here we rotate after the the calculation, since the
