    ‚ćĚ matches ‚ćļ. In this case we know the rotation is safe
    ‚ćĚ because a two character sequence will never have a
    ‚ćĚ match at the last character of a line.
    acc+‚Üź¬Į1‚äĖ‚ćļ√ó'^|'‚ć∑cur

